# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Important: DO NOT IGNORE (explicitly included)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# These should be committed to the repository

# Configuration (edit locally but commit template)
!RoFormer_Communication_Pipeline/config.py
!RoFormer_Communication_Pipeline/requirements.txt

# Scripts and source code
!RoFormer_Communication_Pipeline/*.py
!FYP_Hand_Viz/Assets/Scripts/*.cs

# Unity Assets
!FYP_Hand_Viz/Assets/**/*.*
!FYP_Hand_Viz/ProjectSettings/**

# Documentation
!README.md
!QUICKSTART.md
!*.md

# Configuration examples
!config.py
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes

# License
!LICENSE
